97022be2ecc90182d92ee0e2a172231b69c8597ab4710c3faaac75c88c4e3d5b403e5e14a5adafd6c9f1b8ab88f95b0bf59ce6af29a1d5995243b9974aca85e7  0001-Core-Fix-test-failure-on-32-bit-architectures.patch
"
